   As quietly as I couldst, I crept from the house without a sound.  Making my way to the frozen lands of Velious, I again set upon the task of bettering myself.  Honing my skills in battle.  I sought solitude.  I sought quiet.<br>
   <br>
  I sought a peace I hadst never known.<br>
 <br>
   I laid waste to the beasts which stood before me.  A lifetime of anger so pent up and hidden comes forth during these times....I lash out with a fury I otherwise do not show.  For all the pain I have felt, I deliver it unto the beasts.  So wrapped in my own thoughts I do not even feel the eyes upon me....but my mind lingers upon the events of the last day.<br>
 <br>
  ...fuzzy images return to me as I swing my blade again and again...A woman, touching my hand at the bar...Another who matched me drink for drink...and waking up as I did...<br>
 <br>
  ...another beast falls to my savagery....<br>
 <br>
 ...Pera, thou dost know better...All thou hast ever known is pain...the pain of the physical, the pain of the mental..the pain of loss and suffering...such enduring pain...the ghosts which haunted him still...all so much pain.........So much solitude...<br>
 <br>
    ..there were some days when he felt he could not stand it...The thoughts of wandering into the forest and laying down to die stayed with him...to end the pain....<br>
..always so very alone..................<br>
 <br>
  ... he wandered back to his Solitude Tree to rest but for a moment before once again raising his sword in battle...he spotted them..faint amidst the snow which didst fall, but to an experienced tracker, evident nonetheless...<br>
 <br>
  ..footprints, and fresh, which didst not belong to him, nor to any of the prety which he fought...<br>
 ..petite...female, soft indent which spoke of elven blood.<br>
no more than 30 minutes old...and yet he had heard nothing.  Perhaps it was the ringing in his ears which blocked the sound, or perhaps he was so lost in his own thoughts he mistook it for the wind...but they were there.  As plain as the sunrise on the Bridge of Karana.<br>
 <br>
  Footprints.  A woman was nearby.  Gone?  Watching?<br>
 He knew not, but he followed them..and they led on................... <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub65.ezboard.com/fvoiceofthedragonfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=88.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub65.ezboard.com/fvoiceofthedragonfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=88.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub65.ezboard.com/fvoiceofthedragonfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=88.topic&start=61&stop=71>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub65.ezboard.com/fvoiceofthedragonfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=88.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub65.ezboard.com/fvoiceofthedragonfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=88.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub65.ezboard.com/fvoiceofthedragonfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=88.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub65.ezboard.com/fvoiceofthedragonfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=88.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub65.ezboard.com/fvoiceofthedragonfrm1.threadControl?topicID=88.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub65.ezboard.com/fvoiceofthedragonfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=88.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub65.ezboard.com/fvoiceofthedragonfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=88.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub65.ezboard.com/BBSFo